# Workspace types — `@br-validators/core`

## Problem

Apps import `@br-validators/core`. Types and runtime live in **`packages/br-validators/dist/`** after `tsup`, not in `src/`.

If `dist/` is missing or stale:

```
Could not find a declaration file for module '@br-validators/core'
```

## Resolution by app

| App | Types (IDE / `tsc`) | Runtime bundle |
|-----|---------------------|----------------|
| `apps/cli` | `tsconfig` `paths` → `../../packages/br-validators/src/index.ts` | Vitest/tsc only — OK |
| `apps/playground` | `paths` → `dist/*.d.ts` | `next.config.mjs` webpack `alias` → `dist/*.js` |

Playground details: see `.cursor/rules/playground-next-core.mdc`.

## Parallel typecheck race (CI)

Root `typecheck` MUST be:

`pnpm --filter @br-validators/core build && pnpm -r --sequential typecheck`

Never run bare `pnpm -r typecheck` at root — parallel `pretypecheck` hooks race on `tsup`.

## Agent MUST after editing `packages/br-validators/src/**`

1. `pnpm --filter @br-validators/core build`
2. `pnpm --filter @br-validators/core test:coverage` (100% required)
3. `pnpm verify`

## Agent MUST NOT

- Add `declare module '@br-validators/core'` shims.
- Point playground `paths` at `src/`.
- Skip core build after new exports/subpaths.
